script(type="text/ng-template", id="video-list.html")
    .ui.container(style='padding: 0; margin-bottom: 1em;')
        a(name='top')
        .ui.two.cards(style='margin-top: .5em; padding: .5rem; margin-bottom: 1em;')
            .card(ng-repeat='v in videos', style='width: calc(50% - 1em); margin-left: .5em; margin-right: .5em;')
                a.img(ng-href="/video-player/{{v.video_path_id}}")
                    img(src='//resource.buzzbuzzenglish.com/image/png/buzz-poster.png')
                .extra(style='background-color: #eee; font-size: 1rem;', ng-cloak) {{v.upload_time}}
                    .ui.star.rating(data-rating="4")
        .ui.segment(ng-show="videoList")
            p(style='font-family:"HYxindipaofu"; font-size: 18px;') 您还没有自己的自拍视频，赶快点击下方按钮去拍摄吧！
        button.btn.btn-block(ng-click='goToVideo()', ng-show="videoList", style='display: inline-block;  background-color: #f7b52a; color: #fff;')
            span(style='font-family:"HYxindipaofu"; font-size: 18px;') 我要录视频
        button.btn.btn-block(ng-click='loadMore()', ng-hide="!more") 加载更多历史
        button.btn.btn-block(ng-disabled="true", ng-if="!more&&top") 没有更多了
        button.btn.btn-block(ng-click='toTop()', ng-if='top') 返回顶部